==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thunderclap
<hw>Thun"der*clap`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sharp burst
of thunder; a sudden report of a discharge of atmospheric
electricity.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Thunderclaps</xex> that make them
quake.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When suddenly the <qex>thunderclap</qex> was heard.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thundercloud</ent>⟦br⟧
